sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User (Mobile / Web)
    participant DNS as Route 53
    participant WAF as AWS WAF
    participant ALB as ALB dev-lb-new
    participant API as ECS Fittbot-Production
    participant RD as ElastiCache Redis
    participant DB as RDS MySQL
    participant Q as Celery Queue (Redis)
    participant W as Celery Worker
    participant EXT as External (Razorpay/OpenAI/FCM)

    U->>DNS: app.fymble.app
    DNS-->>U: ALB IP
    U->>WAF: HTTPS request
    WAF->>ALB: forwarded (passes rules)
    ALB->>API: HTTP :8000

    rect rgb(220,235,255)
        Note over API,RD: Auth + Rate-limit middleware
        API->>RD: jail:{ip}, rl:{ip}:m:{bucket}
        RD-->>API: jail state · counter
    end

    alt Read path (home page, profile, feed)
        API->>RD: home:v2:ustate:{cid}
        alt cache miss (58% of GETs)
            API->>DB: SELECT ...
            DB-->>API: rows
            API->>RD: SETEX home:v2:ustate (cache)
        end
        API-->>U: 200 JSON
    else Payment path (checkout/verify/webhook)
        API->>RD: {prefix}:cmd:{cmdid} (idempotency check)
        API->>Q: LPUSH payments queue
        API-->>U: 202 Accepted
        Q->>W: RPOP task
        W->>EXT: Razorpay API
        EXT-->>W: payment result
        W->>DB: UPDATE orders
        W->>RD: SETEX {prefix}:capture:{pid} (24h TTL)
        W->>RD: PUBLISH user_channel:{cid}
        RD-->>API: pubsub fan-out
        API-->>U: WebSocket: payment_confirmed
    else WebSocket path (live gym buddy, chat)
        U->>ALB: wss://api.fymble.app/ws
        ALB->>API: HTTP upgrade
        API->>RD: SUBSCRIBE gym:{gymid}, live:{cid}
        loop
            EXT-->>API: any event
            API->>RD: PUBLISH channel
            RD->>API: fanned to N subscribers
            API->>U: frame
        end
    end
